column4: Can anyone help me with this error I have: E: Type 'GNU' is not known on line 44 in the source list /etc/apt/sources.list
edit manually /etc/apt/sources.list and search for errors on line 44 (from shell: sudo gedit /etc/apt/sources.list)
- got it. i was looking at line 25 instead of 44. messed up something when i was manually editing the file. its fixed now :)
